name: PORT ISLAND 01
description:
Island_01 is a little island where transporter ships of any shape, size or technology can come for a short break. A chill place where travelers can take some time to rest by the beach or eat some of Island_ 01’s famous hot dogs!
Ships often also come to drop of cargo or for their routine ship maintenance. This island is powered by a huge wind turbine in the center of it. Any extra energy it produces is used to fuel ships that stop by and is also transported to other islands in need.

- Port Island_01 is part 1 of the Port Island series
